"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-29-rookie-watkins-unfazed-olympics-challenge\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France - This summer's Olympic Games will be national 400m champion Deandre Watkins' first senior international competition.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6104017123451634, \"rank\": 0.4797994064484355, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he is seemingly undaunted by the task as he sets his sights on securing a spot in the final of his event.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watkins, who has had an outstanding season so far, produced a massive lifetime best effort of 44.48 seconds to win his first national title in June.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He erased his previous best time of 45.19, which he set in the first round of the competition.\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watkins, coached by Reynaldo Walcott at the Elite Performance Track Club, is the fastest Jamaican in the world this year.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_(footballer,_born_1989)\", \"score\": 0.9561897298989113, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reynaldo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_(footballer,_born_1989)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_(footballer,_born_1989)\"}, {\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Derek_Walcott\", \"score\": 0.999995753279031, \"rank\": 4.219103520135298e-06, \"text\": \"Walcott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", 