urce/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999860809841813, \"rank\": 1.1451717666453526e-05, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Jamaican noted that he is not putting himself under any pressure at the championships and is very relaxed and focused on the task ahead.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9159252335259165, \"rank\": 0.09178862024160397, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just want to go out and have fun and do my best.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being the national champion definitely comes with more responsibility because people will be looking at me to be in the final since I am the national champion, so it definitely comes with more expectations.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The preparations have been going well, and I am fit and healthy,\\\" Watkins said.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He, along with Sean Bailey and JeVaughn Powell, will be representing Jamaica in the men's 400m at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1833, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Bailey\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.081878869223148e-12, \"text\": \"Sean Bailey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Bailey\"}, {\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\", \"score\": 0.9999655147292317, \"rank\": 3.447624913073545e-05, \"text\": \"Powell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\"}, {\"begin\": 1887, \"end\": 1894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999727750396101, \"rank\": 1.4463167897705e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watkins stated that he is very excited to be representing the country at the Olympic Games and is looking forward to a great experience at the event.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am feeling very excited, and things are looking okay so far.\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The village is okay, and I am very comfortable.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am looking forward to competing at my first Olympic Games and just doing my best whenever I step on the track,\\\" Watkins said.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": []}]}"